snippet.title: Mexico, 1921: A Deep Slumber - Release Window Trailer
snippet.description:
Immerse yourself in post revolutionary Mexico City with: Mexico,1921: A Deep Slumber. An emotional and intriguing narrative adventure video game about the awakening of a country coming fall 2024!

Wishlist on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1851090/Mexico_1921_A_Deep_Slumber/
